The city of Ingos
Since the exact location of the magic artifact is unknown, it is necessary to take care of shelter and the possibility of replenishing supplies, repairing weapons and armor. The best place for this is a town, which is located nearby.
#subobj 1
Reach the bridge
The town of Ingos is located on the eastern shore of the lake. You need to cross the river to get to the town.
#subobj 2
Enter the town
Apparently, the province is not very well controlled by the authorities. The road to the town can be dangerous!
